data.description: Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this delightful 3 bed/1 bath home yours. With its fully fenced yard for outdoor gatherings and a serene setting to enjoy the sunset, it provides the perfect combination of comfort and convenience in the heart of Salem. Living room with fireplace, 3rd bedroom off of master could also be used as bonus room/office. Full bathroom with ample space. Large backyard with fruit trees. Contact us today to schedule a private viewing and see all that this property has to offer!
